# RewriteAI 🪄

A minimalist macOS menu bar utility that uses Google Gemini (or local LLMs) to rewrite selected text instantly using system-wide hotkeys.

## Features
- **Global Context:** Works in any app (TextEdit, Chrome, Slack) via Accessibility APIs.
- **AI Engines:** Supports Gemini 3 Flash and Gemini 1.5.
- **Privacy First:** Uses a secure Shield Window to prevent UI interference during processing.
- **Customizable:** Securely store your own API keys in the app settings.

## Getting Started
1. Clone the repo.
2. Open `RewriteAI.xcodeproj` in Xcode 17+.
3. Build and Run.
4. **Important:** Enable Accessibility permissions in *System Settings > Privacy & Security* to allow text replacement.

